4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course that prepares students for a career in tech's highest-paying fields. The course has a duration of 16 weeks and includes 3 classes per week, with a maximum class size of 12 people. No previous experience is needed, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python and libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. They will also work with supervised and unsupervised learning models, and solve real-life cases. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. The course is taught by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). Stop.